						<div class="postbody">In paltformers can we use sprite 0 hit flag to find out if the character is grounded(on a platform) or not? What all can sprite 0 hit detection be used for?</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Cheers,
<br />Nadia</div>
