					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You can, but it's a pretty dangerous thing to rely on Sprite 0 hits for such a thing; it's too limiting.
<br />
<br />For one, your hit/polling loop might take up most of the screen time if your platform is near the bottom of the screen.  Your code will be practically idle for much of the valuable processing time.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.chrismcovell.com">http://www.chrismcovell.com</a><!-- m --></div>
