				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Sprite zero hit should NEVER be used as a form of logical collision detection.  
<br />
<br />Its only use is to split the screen at a specific point, or if you need to know when the vblank period ends, you can force a sprite 0 collision, but not directly poll it.</div>

					
