					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Seems to me that Sprite Hit 0 was just a cheap way of allowing raster effects on the base hardware rather than including some sort of built in scanline counter like they probably should have done. There really is no other use for it than attempting to time code to interact with rendering in some way. Logical game operations should never rely on that.</div>

